Title: Empty "Monitoring on Host field" deleteds all Wato config
Component: wato
Class: bug
State: done
Date: 2012-09-04 11:35:16
Targetversion: 1.2.0

In replicated wato settings all configuration get lost, when the Monitoring on host field is empty on creating a host

2012-09-24 16:03:22: changed state open -> done
It is not possible to select an empty value in "monitored on". So this bug has been fixed.
